# de_utils v2 — Data Engineering Utility Library

> A batteries-included Python library for Azure ADLS Gen2, Hive Metastore, Spark ETL,
> Data Quality, Lineage Tracking, Delta Lake, Job Checkpointing, and Medallion Architecture.

